==Venues==
Santa Cruz and Tarija are the main venues of the tournament. Montero was announced as an extra venue days before the start of the tournament.<ref name=venues>{{cite web|title=Montero, another venue for the U-15 Sudamericano|url=http://www.conmebol.com/en/content/montero-another-venue-u-15-sudamericano|publisher=CONMEBOL|accessdate=29 November 2013|language=Spanish}}</ref> 
