==Referees==
On October 23, 2013 a referee and an assistant referee from each country where chosen for the tournament.<ref name=referees>{{cite web|last=Figueroa Britez|first=Francisco|title=Convocatoria de Arbitros|url=http://www.conmebol.com/sites/default/files/arbitros_sub-15.pdf|publisher=CONMEBOL|accessdate=29 November 2013|language=Spanish}}</ref> 

