==Final Round==
The final stage is scheduled to take place between 28 November and 30 November.<ref>{{cite web|title=Calendario de Partidos|url=http://www.conmebol.com/sites/default/files/fixture_sudamericano_sub-15_masculino.pdf|publisher=conmebol.com|accessdate=20 September 2010|page=6|format=pdf}}</ref> 

